# LegacyCraft DevKit - method mappings (SRG format)
# Format: MD: <obfClass>/<obfMethod> <obfDesc> <deobfClass>/<deobfMethod> <deobfDesc>
#
# Empty for now. Method mappings need a verified semantic role just like
# fields; obfuscated method names like a/b/c reuse a single short name
# across many methods in the same class, so naming them safely requires
# more context than can be inferred from a single class. Add entries here
# as their meaning is verified.
